  N2 --> N3{PB: Process Builder - Enforce documentation requirements.}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4{PB: Process Builder - Process pre-authorization requests.}
  N4 --> N5[PB: Notification - Notify dealer of claim status.]
  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced manual handling, accelerated claim processing, improved OTIF metrics, and standardized front-end compliance.]
  N3 -->|Incomplete documentation detected.| B1[Reject claim and request additional documentation.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Claim is returned to dealer for additional information.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|High-cost repair requires pre-authori...| B2[Escalate claim for further review.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Claim is escalated for detailed review and potential approval.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Claim meets all criteria.| B3[Approve claim and proceed with processing.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Claim is approved and processed for payment.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]